details.biography:
Bianca Bosch is an American film and television actress, model, and social media influencer. She is known for her portrayal of Olivia in film series The Kissing Booth. She also appeared in Killer Instinct with Chris Hansen in 2017.

Bianca Bosch was born on January 26, 1996 in South Africa. Her family moved to Los Angeles, California when she was a little child. Her father is a businessman, and her mother is a household. She did her graduation from the University of United States.  Bosch began her career as an actress with the television series Killer Instinct along with Chris Hansen in the year 2017. In the year 2018, she starred in the Netflix Original film The Kissing Booth, played the role of Olivia in 2020 and 2021.
details.name: Bianca Bosch
